==词汇==
景颇语词汇有大量[[藏缅语族|藏缅语族]]词汇和非藏缅词汇，主要有[[缅甸语|缅甸语]]和[[掸语|掸语]]。<ref name=":0">{{Cite journal|last=Kurabe|first=Keita|date=2016-12-31|title=Phonology of Burmese loanwords in Jinghpaw|url=https://repository.kulib.kyoto-u.ac.jp/dspace/handle/2433/219015|journal=Kyoto University Linguistic Research|volume=35|doi=10.14989/219015|issn=1349-7804|access-date=2021-06-20|archive-date=2020-12-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201216072230/https://repository.kulib.kyoto-u.ac.jp/dspace/handle/2433/219015|dead-url=no}}</ref>{{Rp|91–128}}缅甸语借词有两个层次，较老的层次反映书面缅语，较新的层次反映现代缅甸语音系。<ref name=":0" />较老层次有取道掸语来的缅甸语词汇，同样展现古代的音系和词义。<ref name=":0" />景颇语还从掸语借来大量词汇，景颇语和掸语有长达几个世纪的接触。<ref>{{Cite journal|last=Kurabe|first=Keita|date=2017|title=A Classified Lexicon of Shan Loanwords in Jinghpaw|url=http://repository.tufs.ac.jp/bitstream/10108/89212/2/aall011011-final.pdf|journal=Asian and African Languages and Linguistics|volume=11|access-date=2021-06-20|archive-date=2021-06-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210608223750/http://repository.tufs.ac.jp/bitstream/10108/89212/2/aall011011-final.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>景颇语作为缅甸北部高原地区的通用语，常常是同区域语言借词的源头，[[拉旺语|拉旺语]]和[[载瓦语|载瓦语]]等语言中有大量景颇语借词。<ref name=":0" />

